    <!-- VM Tutorial / FAQ / About / Shortcuts -->
    <sys:String x:Key="VM.Tutorial">Insight Training Studio Tutorial
─────────────────────

■ Quick Mode
  1. Drag &amp; drop files or use the file select button to import materials
  2. Set speaker, resolution, speed, etc.
  3. Click "Generate" to auto-create video

■ Detailed Editor (Main Window)
  1. Click "+ Add" in the left panel to add scenes
  2. Click "Select" to set images/videos
  3. Enter narration text
  4. Click "Play Audio" to preview
  5. Set subtitle text and style
  6. Click "Export Video" to generate

■ Text Overlay
  Place custom text on each scene.
  Set position (X/Y%), size, color, and alignment individually.
  Use "Cover Template" to add title + subtitle at once.

■ Templates
  Save and load settings like BGM, watermark, and resolution as templates.

■ PPTX Import
  Drop a PowerPoint file to auto-create scenes from slides.
  (Requires Trial plan or above)</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="VM.Tutorial.Title">Tutorial</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="VM.FAQ">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)
─────────────────────

Q: Cannot connect to VOICEVOX.
A: Make sure the VOICEVOX engine is running.
   Connection is configured during the initial setup wizard.

Q: Video export fails.
A: Ensure FFmpeg is installed and included in your PATH.
   A warning is shown at startup if FFmpeg is not found.

Q: How do I enter a license key?
A: Go to menu "Help" → "License Manager".

Q: Subtitles and transitions are unavailable.
A: These require a Trial plan or above. Go to "Help" → "License Manager"
   to activate your license.

Q: What file formats are supported?
A: Images: PNG, JPG, BMP, GIF / Videos: MP4, AVI, MOV, WMV, MKV
   Audio (BGM): MP3, WAV, OGG, FLAC, AAC, M4A
   Other: PPTX, TXT, MD

Q: How do I cancel an export?
A: Click the "Cancel" button next to the progress bar.

Q: Where are templates saved?
A: In %LOCALAPPDATA%\InsightCast\Templates.

Q: How do I contact support?
A: Email support@harmonic-insight.com.</sys:String>
